Correlation analysis



Xuất report.



====================================
PHASE 2
FEATURE ENGINEERING
====================================


Tạo:

feature_engineering.py



Implement:


================================

1. TIME FEATURES

================================


Convert:

trans_date_trans_time



Create:


transaction_hour


transaction_day


transaction_month


transaction_weekday



Create:


is_night_transaction



Rule:


00:00 - 05:00 = 1



================================

2. CUSTOMER FEATURES

================================


From:


dob



Create:


customer_age



================================

3. LOCATION FEATURES

================================


Using:


lat

long


merch_lat

merch_long



Calculate:



distance_customer_merchant



using Haversine formula



================================

4. TRANSACTION FEATURES

================================


Using:


amt



Create:


log_amount


amount_zscore



================================

5. CATEGORY FEATURES

================================


Use:


merchant

category

gender

state

job

city



Encoding:


OneHotEncoder



================================

6. DROP COLUMNS

================================


Remove:


cc_num

first

last

street

trans_num

dob

trans_date_trans_time



Reason:

Avoid data leakage.



====================================
PHASE 3
STATISTICAL DETECTION
====================================


Create:


statistical.py



Implement:



Z-score:


Function:


detect_zscore()



Rule:


abs(z_score) > 3



Return:


prediction

anomaly_score



--------------------------------



IQR:


Function:


detect_iqr()



Rule:


value < Q1 - 1.5*IQR


or


value > Q3 + 1.5*IQR



Return:


prediction

score



====================================
PHASE 4
MACHINE LEARNING MODELS
====================================


Train:


fraudTrain.csv



Test:


fraudTest.csv



Dataset imbalance:

Fraud cases are rare.


Use:


class_weight="balanced"

where available.



================================

MODEL 1

Isolation Forest


File:


isolation_forest.py



Use:


sklearn.ensemble.IsolationForest



Implement:


train()

predict()

save()

load()



Output:


1 = normal


-1 = anomaly



================================

MODEL 2

One-Class SVM


File:


one_class_svm.py



Use:


sklearn.svm.OneClassSVM



Kernel:


rbf



Implement:


train()

predict()



================================

MODEL 3

Local Outlier Factor


File:


lof.py



Use:


sklearn.neighbors.LocalOutlierFactor



Implement:


train()

predict()



====================================
PHASE 5
MODEL EVALUATION
====================================


Create:


evaluate.py



Compare:


Z-score

IQR

Isolation Forest

One-Class SVM

LOF



Metrics:


Precision

Recall

F1-score

ROC-AUC

Confusion Matrix



Important:


Không đánh giá bằng Accuracy vì dataset imbalance.



Save:


model_results.csv



Format:


Model

Precision

Recall

F1

ROC-AUC



